data.description: Discover the allure of 17 North Central Avenue in the historic community of Jamestown. This property, set on an expansive 1.3-acre lot, features 2 bedrooms with 3 full bathrooms, walk-in closets, and a rear deck. The home seamlessly blends classic charm with modern convenience. With a large yard, this is an ideal space for both relaxation and expansion opportunities.
